OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will clear northeast through the
OL,7,Fevening. Then it will stay dry for the
OL,8,Frest of the night with clear spells
OL,9,Fand perhaps the odd fog patch by dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,12,Fpossible at first, but soon clouding
OL,13,Fover with showery outbreaks of rain,
OL,14,Fthese turning heavy in places in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Much less warm than Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
